    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire an automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained with an uncompromising attention to detail, the exterior retains its original luster while the interior remains in an immaculate, factory-fresh state. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance and aesthetic perfection. For the discerning individual who accepts only the finest, this specimen stands as a definitive example of luxury and care.",
      "price": 46500.0,
