      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection, this is it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
