    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is a superlative example of the E46 M3, a vehicle that represents the zenith of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously overhauled to ensure precise valve timing across the entire 8,000 RPM powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering tactile engagement through a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This chassis remains structurally impeccable, with documented preventative subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing high-durometer bushings to preserve factory kinematics. Finished in its original factory coating with zero paint meter discrepancies, the exterior matches a cockpit free of bolster wear or delamination. This is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen optimized for the purist seeking peak mechanical harmony and lateral acceleration capability.",
